            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">Chicago Socialist, compiler of list of Socialist publications, 1900-1950. The papers contain correspondence including letters from socialist notables, material relating to the Young People’s Socialist League; a scrapbook of articles by Halushka and others; a scrapbook relating to the Young Circle League; and survey forms and charts relating to Halushka’s research on Socialist mayors and Socialist newspapers.</abstract>
            <origination label="creator">
                <persname source="local">Halushka, Mendel V., 1904-1958.</persname>
            </origination>
        </did>
        <custodhist id="ref4">
